+/**
+ * Request INTEL_SIP_SMC_ASYNC_POLL
+ * Async call used by service driver at EL1 to query mailbox response from SDM.
+ *
+ * Call register usage:
+ * a0 INTEL_SIP_SMC_ASYNC_POLL
